    recipe: `1. Bruise lemongrass and slice galangal. Simmer in broth and coconut milk 10 min to infuse.\n2. Add chicken, mushrooms, lime leaves, and chili peppers. Cook 10 min until chicken is done.\n3. Season with fish sauce, lime juice, and brown sugar.\n4. Taste and adjust — it should be creamy, sour, and slightly spicy.\n5. Ladle into bowls, top with cilantro and extra lime.`,
