    recipe: `1. Fry garlic and ginger in a splash of sesame oil until fragrant.\n2. Add broth and bring to a simmer.\n3. Whisk miso paste with a ladleful of hot broth until smooth, then stir into pot. Do not boil.\n4. Add butter, stir to melt.\n5. Cook noodles per package, divide into bowls.\n6. Ladle miso broth over.\n7. Top with pork belly, egg, corn, bamboo shoots, nori, sesame seeds, and scallions.`,
