    recipe: `1. Dice tuna into small ½-inch cubes. Keep cold.\n2. Dice avocado and cucumber similarly.\n3. Mix soy sauce, sesame oil, lime juice, ginger, jalapeño, and sriracha.\n4. Toss tuna gently with dressing.\n5. Fold in avocado and cucumber.\n6. Plate with wonton crisps, top with scallions and sesame seeds.\n7. Serve immediately.`,
